question: In order to facilitate the life of students at the university and their movements to and from the university at lectures’ times, especially for the residences located far from the university, we kindly ask you to fill in the form below to count the number of students residing in the following residences: Melana Apartments, Melawis Apartments, Desa Skudai Apartments, The Garden Residences. Based on the number, arrangements will be made with the university authorities to provide buses that pass to / from the aforementioned residences during lecture times.
